-- Sinopec Changling Completes Crude Unit's Construction; Ready for Trial Run
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-12T03:32:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/sinopec-changling-completes-crude-unit-s-construction-ready-for-trial-run.html
China Petroleum & Chemical Corp. has
completed construction of an 8 million metric-ton-a-year crude
distillation unit at its Changling plant, parent China
Petrochemical Corp. said in a statement on its website dated
yesterday. The crude unit is ready for trial runs, according to
the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Winnie Zhu in Shanghai at 
